This paper discusses a machine learning algorithm, specifically the naive Bayes classifier, and proposes a modification to improve its performance. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also mentions experimental results on image classification (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL), indicating that these sub-categories are also relevant.
